{"tid":644894,"cid":31,"subCid":7,"title":"[耶穌學佛]- 連登大碟《耶和佛》","createTime":"2018-04-27T15:01:31.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-12T04:10:11.000Z","uid":17232,"like":79,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":28,"replies":[{"pid":"0dd33fedaafe3debbe94f1b326144b2584c148a6","tid":644894,"uid":17232,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-04-27T15:01:31.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: green;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">連登大碟《耶和佛》棄信耶穌，轉信佛</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">原曲：幸福之歌</span><br />\n<br />\n<strong>輕輕鬆鬆跟我去學佛<br />\n釋迦經中深深的教訓<br />\n唸著唸著笑說我主低能<br />\n<br />\n一天一天修習這聖諦<br />\n一點一點嗤笑那上帝<br />\n誰竟會相信這篇章節太入世<br />\n<br />\n何時令你相信主 經裡的<br />\n荊棘佈滿叢林徑<br />\n天主身上的傷口 是警惕<br />\n<br />\n然而佛看到聖經 也都嘆息<br />\n釋迦也無力 想去認證<br />\n天堂能更比淨土超脫心境<br />\n<br />\n*唱著梵音之歌<br />\n我佛妙音環播<br />\n無數遍清淨的經文與佛相<br />\n<br />\n梵音傳誦經章<br />\n耽於頃刻無常的閃亮<br />\n愛恨苦惱別離領教此生<br />\n七日中天道眾生 誰洗淨業障*<br />\n<br />\n身邊冤親多彰顯惡果<br />\n反省今生的所有犯錯<br />\n你我每個結局或會錯摸<br />\n<br />\n曾深思足跡星系大千裡<br />\n耶穌今天終找出了實據<br />\n隨即意識到世間一剎過萬歲<br />\n<br />\n重逢佛法可以麼 我可以麼<br />\n釋迦說你來盤坐<br />\n天主感謝他釋出 大藏經<br />\n<br />\n隨緣遇上這佛聲 立即靜聽<br />\n聲音裡尋覓 這世道裡<br />\n娑婆仍猶像淨土思緒幽清<br />\n<br />\nRepeat*<br />\n<br />\n耶和華信佛陀 各界信徒即將干戈<br />\n逢禮拜日去打齋好過<br />\n忘掉經課 投入那貧僧的心態超越境界<br />\n<br />\nRepeat*<br />\n<br />\n想像於天國我主能跟我唸唱</strong><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">求巴打幫手唱出黎整MV<br />\n大碟更多內容會喺稍後公佈</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span>"},{"pid":"345e4abbe1705513c806e52f9bea7bee6fe20483","tid":644894,"uid":136448,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-27T15:04:31.000Z","msg":"高質<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n推"},{"pid":"af80df36d5ca666c031819e220943a2deecbeda7","tid":644894,"uid":17232,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-27T15:13:54.000Z","msg":"推到有人唱<br />\n暫名：梵音之歌<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ea08229ebfb8926a797010d2c67f3ebc255d7516","tid":644894,"uid":140979,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-27T15:16:26.000Z","msg":"正評+推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0100c1e9975bd6e8fed0bc677716429702c750e5","tid":644894,"uid":140979,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-27T15:19:10.000Z","msg":"竟然無人睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a8d02c1717b43ab45f63caa9f06ffb7ef5a17249","tid":644894,"uid":46435,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-27T15:21:42.000Z","msg":"連登無人玩改歌嫁啦 算啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f664ee2cd7f7b1ff1fca7c8cc3deb0bcebbf080a","tid":644894,"uid":17232,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-27T15:23:11.000Z","msg":"完全無人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我自己推算數"},{"pid":"115236c7eb6180461e9e42483e618fe85ab547f4","tid":644894,"uid":17232,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-27T15:24:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a83a997f2f393a727b10ceb1402ddcf57b8d5a6